	Locking an object in the tree causes GUI crash.

2010-02-18  vadim  <vadim@vk.crocodile.org>

	* FWWindow.cpp (FWWindow::FWWindow): fixed #1252 The "New
	Object"-Dialog is always opened up twice when pressing <CTRL>+<N>

